  "_comment": "Model→URL registry for vendor product photos. Slugs are lowercased+non-alphanumeric→'_'. Service tries this URL first, falls back to a generated SVG chassis image when the URL fails or is null. The SVG renderer is the primary mechanism — it produces distinct, accurate-to-spec images for every printer (correct chassis type, build volume, feature badges) without depending on unstable vendor CDNs. Admins can populate any URL here OR upload a custom image via POST /api/printer-image/:slug.",
